function _fallback() internal {
    _willFallback();
    address impl = _implementation();
    require(AddressUtils.isContract(impl), "Implementation is not a contract");
    _delegate(impl);
}
```

Note that this fix introduces a gas overhead for every call made through the proxy due to the `extcodesize` operation.

